versions.correctionNotice: A minor error was identified in tables REC1 and REC2, in the Public Sector Finances released at 09:30am on 21st September 2016. A processing error led to the publication of incorrect data for 2014 for series ANRS and associated series ANRV, JW34 and JW38 which are derived from ANRS. These series have now been corrected. We apologise for any inconvenience.

versions.correctionNotice: A minor error was identified in table REC2 in the Public Sector Finances released at 09:30am on 21st September 2016. A processing error led to the publication of incorrect data for 2015/16 for series ANRS and associated series ANRV, ANSI, ANSL, ANSV, ANSY, JW34 and JW37 which are derived from ANRS. These series have now been corrected leading to revisions to tables REC1, PSA10 and Public Sector Finances borrowing by sub-sector, in 2015/16. Measures of net borrowing, net cash requirement and net debt are unaffected by these changes.  We apologise for any inconvenience.
